MIT Java Wordnet Interface 1.1

Packages
edu.mit.jwi.content Provides classes and interfaces that can parse and manipulate lines from the Wordnet data files.
edu.mit.jwi.content.compare Provides classes that encode the sorting order of the Wordnet data file lines, to enable binary searching.
edu.mit.jwi.content.parse Provides classes and interfaces that deal with parsing individual lines from Wordnet data files.
edu.mit.jwi.data Provides classes and interfaces for the creation and control dictionary data files.
edu.mit.jwi.dict Provides the main dictionary interface and a default implementation.
edu.mit.jwi.item Provides classes and interfaces that represent the Wordnet data structures.
edu.mit.jwi.morph Provides several simple classes that can be used to find the stems of words using Wordnet.
